;; kadode 門出 — seed labor-exit graph (real, PUBLIC Japanese labour law only)
;; ADR-2606112238 · vocabulary: labor-exit-ontology (00-contracts/schemas/labor-exit-ontology.kotoba.edn)
;;
;; SCOPE GUARD (constitutional, G1 — read first):
;;   - kadode is a 使者 (messenger) + concierge, NEVER a 代理人 (agent) and NEVER the practice of
;;     law. It RELAYS a worker's already-formed unilateral resignation (民法627 = unilateral
;;     right, employer consent NOT required) and DRAFTS the worker's own documents. It does NOT
;;     and CANNOT negotiate terms / severance / settlements (弁護士法72条 非弁行為禁止). Anything
;;     needing negotiation is routed to :route/union (団体交渉) or :route/lawyer.
;;   - A ground / citation / risk-counter is a DISCLOSED legal fact (N3), never a kadode verdict;
;;     kadode never promises an outcome.
;;
;; SOURCING: all grounds are :authoritative public statutes (e-Gov 法令検索 / 厚労省). The scenario
;;   ↔ route mapping is :representative procedural guidance, NOT legal advice for a specific case.
;;   Coverage of all employment situations is bounded by design (G5). Live relay/sending is
;;   G7-gated.

